'''巴西－伊朗關係'''，是指[[巴西聯邦共和國|巴西聯邦共和國]]和[[伊朗伊斯蘭共和國|伊朗伊斯蘭共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。两国之间的交流与往来始于1903年，巴西和伊朗兩國關係一向非常友好，在經濟和政治等各方面均有合作<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.payvand.com/news/10/may/1179.html |title=Iran, Brazil agree to boost trade ties to $10 billion |publisher=Payvand.com |date=2006-11-22 |accessdate=2010-05-23 |archive-date=2011-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111125042329/http://www.payvand.com/news/10/may/1179.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；然而[[巴西總統|巴西總統]][[迪爾瑪·羅塞夫|迪爾瑪·羅塞夫]]當選後，巴西經常批評伊朗違反人權和公民權利，引致兩國關係大大惡化<ref name=starter>{{cite news | url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/04/05/opinion/gomez-iran-brazil-chill/index.html | work=CNN | title=Why Iran-Brazil friendship has gone cold | date=5 April 2012 | accessdate=2014-07-14 | archive-date=2012-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419173515/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/04/05/opinion/gomez-iran-brazil-chill/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 概況 ==
近年來，巴西和伊朗兩國關係一向非常友好。儘管對伊朗因[[伊朗核問題|核問題]]而受到{{link-en|國際對伊朗的制裁|Sanctions against Iran|國際制裁}}，但巴西政府認為，應是由[[國際原子能機構|國際原子能機構]]而非[[聯合國安理會|聯合國安理會]]解決爭議<ref name="Iran 2008">"Brazil Doesn’t Recognize Unilateral Sanctions on Iran," Tehran Times, November 10, 2008.</ref>。2007年9月，時任巴西總統[[路易斯·伊納西奧·盧拉·達席爾瓦|路易斯·伊納西奧·盧拉·達席爾瓦]]指出伊朗有進行和平核研究的權利，不應因為西方國家的懷疑而受到懲罰，而且伊朗至今仍未曾違反聯合國對核武器的規定<ref>"Brazil’s Lula Defends Iran’s Nuclear Rights," Reuters, September 25, 2007.</ref>。於2008年11月，巴西外長[[塞爾索·阿莫林|塞爾索·阿莫林]]重申政府的觀點，指巴西不承認對伊朗實施的單方面制裁，又指伊朗政府應充分與國際原子能機構合作，從而避免受到制裁<ref name="Iran 2008"/>。2010年2月，有傳言指巴西一直有舉行雙邊會談，在會談中向伊朗提供武器級[[鈾|鈾]]，指巴西無在與伊朗舉行的任何會談期間談及會向伊朗提供濃縮鈾<ref>"Brazil Not in Talks to Enrich Iran’s Uranium," Wall Street Journal, February 3, 2010.</ref>。

於2010年5月17日，巴西、伊朗和[[土耳其|土耳其]]三國發布了《德黑蘭宣言》，其中伊朗同意向土耳其輸出低濃縮鈾，以換取{{link-en|核研究反應堆|Research reactor}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/8686728.stm|title=Nuclear fuel declaration by Iran, Turkey and Brazil|date=17 May 2010|publisher=BBC|accessdate=28 May 2010|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805194019/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/8686728.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2010-05/17/c_13298700.htm |title=''Xinhua English News'': Iran to sign nuclear swap deal with Turkey, Brazil |access-date=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2016-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018130036/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2010-05/17/c_13298700.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管國際社會普遍支持<ref>{{cite web |url=http://arabnews.com/saudiarabia/article56993.ece |title=GCC backs efforts to solve Iran N-issue |publisher=Arab News |date=24 May 2010 |accessdate=2 August 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100701132741/http://arabnews.com/saudiarabia/article56993.ece |archivedate=2010年7月1日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/article.asp?edition_id=1&categ_id=2&article_id=115187#axzz0p9YebQlj |title=Politics – Hariri heads to Washington after visits to Egypt, Turkey |publisher=The Daily Star |date=24 May 2010 |accessdate=2 August 2010 |archive-date=2010-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100909054416/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/article.asp?edition_id=1&categ_id=2&article_id=115187#axzz0p9YebQlj |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Rebhi |first=Abdullah |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5h9KwVkudAQRrSrs6770IeK56BgoA |title=AFP: Merkel urges Iran to 'carefully consider' nuclear deal |publisher=Google |date=27 May 2010 |accessdate=2 August 2010 |archive-date=2013-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130201195308/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5h9KwVkudAQRrSrs6770IeK56BgoA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/china/2010-05/25/c_13315355.htm|title=China calls for peaceful solution to Iranian nuclear issue|date=25 May 2010|publisher=Xinhua|accessdate=26 May 2010|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018125927/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/china/2010-05/25/c_13315355.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此方案受到了[[美國|美國]]和[[以色列|以色列]]的指責，美國更宣佈將會建議對伊朗實施更多制裁，迫使她結束核濃縮項目<ref name="businessweek.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-05-18/clinton-says-russia-china-u-s-back-iran-sanctions-update4-.html |title=Clinton Says Russia, China, U.S. Back Iran Sanctions (Update4) |work=BusinessWeek |date=18 May 2010 |accessdate=2 August 2010 |archive-date=2011-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628195112/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-05-18/clinton-says-russia-china-u-s-back-iran-sanctions-update4-.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；土耳其和巴西批評美國此舉<ref name="businessweek.com"/>，巴西外長又對美國的立場表示遺憾，指巴西反對制裁<ref name="todayszaman1">{{cite web|url=http://www.todayszaman.com/tz-web/news-213822-brazil-vents-frustration-with-west-over-iran-deal.html |title=Brazil vents frustration with West over Iran deal |publisher=Todayszaman.com |date=22 June 2010 |accessdate=2 August 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100625061044/http://todayszaman.com/tz-web/news-213822-brazil-vents-frustration-with-west-over-iran-deal.html |archivedate=2010-06-25}}</ref>。

迪爾瑪·羅塞夫當選巴西總統後，巴西政府改變了對伊朗的政策，兩國關係冷卻。羅塞夫嚴厲地批評伊朗的人權狀況，又在她的競選活動指出，伊朗行[[石刑|石刑]]的做法是「[[中世紀|中世紀]]的行為」<ref>{{cite news | url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/04/05/opinion/gomez-iran-brazil-chill/index.html | work=CNN | title=Why Iran-Brazil friendship has gone cold | date=5 April 2012 | accessdate=2014-07-14 | archive-date=2012-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419173515/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/04/05/opinion/gomez-iran-brazil-chill/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴西又支持{{link-en|聯合國特別報告員|United Nations Special Rapporteur}}對伊朗侵犯人權的譴責<ref>[http://thinkprogress.org/security/2012/01/24/410350/amid-pressure-and-threats-irans-isolation-grows-with-cooled-brazil-relations/?mobile=nc Amid Pressure And Threats, Iran’s Isolation Grows With Cooled Brazil Relations] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221171910/http://thinkprogress.org/security/2012/01/24/410350/amid-pressure-and-threats-irans-isolation-grows-with-cooled-brazil-relations/?mobile=nc |date=2015-02-21 }} ThinkProgress. Retrieved on 2012-09-12.</ref>。其後，伊朗總統內賈德的媒體顧問{{link-en|Ali Akbar Javanfekr|Ali Akbar Javanfekr}}指羅塞夫破壞了多年的良好關係<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/01/24/world/americas/ahmadinejad-adviser-accuses-brazil-of-ruining-relations.html | work=The New York Times | first=Simon | last=Romero | title=Ahmadinejad Adviser Accuses Brazil of Ruining Relations | date=23 January 2012 | accessdate=2014-07-14 | archive-date=2021-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226135845/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/01/24/world/americas/ahmadinejad-adviser-accuses-brazil-of-ruining-relations.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他後來否認曾作上述表示<ref>[http://www.mfa.ir/NewsShow.aspx?id=2972&menu=108&lang=en Foreign Ministry Spokesman Ramin Mehmanparast said on Friday Tehran and Brasilia enjoy ancient-old ties, calling for enhanced cooperation] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130218211443/http://www.mfa.ir/NewsShow.aspx?id=2972&menu=108&lang=en |date=2013-02-18 }} Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Iran. Retrieved on 2012-09-12.</ref>。

2012年4月，伊朗駐巴西大使館[[外交官|外交官]]Hekmatollah Ghorbani遭控猥褻侵犯一群9-15歲的年輕女孩<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-17780497 "Iranian Diplomat Accused of Brazil Child Molestation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-17780497 |date=20201112013627 }}, "BBC News", 20 April 2012</ref>。當時發現這名外交官在[[巴西利亞|巴西利亞]]一所[[俱樂部|俱樂部]]的[[游泳池|游泳池]]不當觸摸一名女孩<ref name="stumbleupon.com">Saeed Kamali Dehghan, [http://www.stumbleupon.com/su/5Ysbjk/www.rawstory.com/rs/2012/04/20/iranian-diplomat-accused-of-child-molestation-in-brazil/ "The Raw Story: Iranian Diplomat Accused"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.stumbleupon.com/su/5Ysbjk/www.rawstory.com/rs/2012/04/20/iranian-diplomat-accused-of-child-molestation-in-brazil/ |date=20150924111306 }}, "The Guardian", 20 April 2012</ref>。很多巴西人對此感到憤怒，但伊朗駐巴西大使館指出猥褻侵犯的指控是文化觀念差異導致誤解<ref name="stumbleupon.com"/>，而巴西外長{{link-en|安東尼奧·帕特里奧塔|Antonio Patriota}}對事件表示厭惡和失望<ref>Saeed Kamali Dehghan, [http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/iran-blog/2012/apr/20/iran-diplomat-accused-molestation-brazil "Iranian Diplomat Accused of Child Molestation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/iran-blog/2012/apr/20/iran-diplomat-accused-molestation-brazil |date=20130115040512 }}, "The Guardian", 20 April 2012</ref>。該名外交官其後因[[外交豁免權|外交豁免權]]而離開巴西<ref>[http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/04/25/accused-of-molesting-children-iranian-diplomat-leaves-brazil/ "Accused of Molesting Children, Iranian Diplomat Leaves Brazil"] {{Wayback|url=http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/04/25/accused-of-molesting-children-iranian-diplomat-leaves-brazil/ |date=20140810084716 }}, "Global Voices", 25 April 2012</ref>，而[[伊朗外交部|伊朗外交部]]最終發表聲明，指該名外交官違反了行政法規和伊斯蘭道德<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-18153554 | work=BBC News | title=Iran sacks diplomat accused of Brazil pool abuse | date=21 May 2012 | accessdate=2014-07-14 | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111180254/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-18153554 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 經貿關係 ==
於2011年，巴西是伊朗在在[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]的最大貿易夥伴，該年兩國之間的雙邊貿易總額為$23.3億[[美元|美元]]，比上年增長5%<ref name="MDIC">[http://www.mdic.gov.br//sitio/interna/interna.php?area=5&menu=2477&refr=576 ''Comércio Exterior: Irã, República Islâmica do''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mdic.gov.br//sitio/interna/interna.php?area=5&menu=2477&refr=576 |date=20190519082928 }} ''Ministério do Desenvolvimento, Indústria e Comércio Exterior''. Retrieved on 2012-01-29.</ref>。巴西出口到伊朗的產品包括[[食物|食物]]、[[藥物|藥物]]、[[礦物|礦物]]和[[汽車|汽車]]等<ref name="Preiss">[http://www.cemoc.com.ar/ANMO%201%20-%203%20Relacoes%20Brasil.pdf ''"As Relações Brasil-Irã: dos antecedentes aos desdobramentos no século XXI"''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715013902/http://www.cemoc.com.ar/ANMO%201%20-%203%20Relacoes%20Brasil.pdf |date=2014-07-15 }} ("Brazil-Iran relations: from its beginning to the developments of the 21st century") Preiss, José Luiz Silva. ''Faculdade Anglo-Americano''. Retrieved on 2012-01-29.</ref>，伊朗更是巴西在2011年最大的[[牛肉|牛肉]]出口市場<ref>[http://www.turquoisepartners.com/iraninvestment/IIM-Oct11.pdf Iran Investment] {{Wayback|url=http://www.turquoisepartners.com/iraninvestment/IIM-Oct11.pdf |date=20120320012036 }} Turquoise Partners. Retrieved on 2012-09-12.</ref>。[[巴西石油股份有限公司|巴西石油股份有限公司]]於近幾年大量地投資伊朗[[石油|石油]]和[[天然氣|天然氣]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irantracker.org/global-business-in-iran?country=728&contractor=All&client=All&sector=All&amount=0&status=All&apply-block=Refine |title=Projects | Global Business in Iran |publisher=Irantracker.org |date= |accessdate=2010-05-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720024436/http://www.irantracker.org/global-business-in-iran?country=728&contractor=All&client=All&sector=All&amount=0&status=All&apply-block=Refine |archivedate=2011-07-20 }}</ref>。

